B.M1=new A.aN(B.c2,"\u2708\ufe0f Reading Tips",'Watch for question types:\n\u2022 **"What is the main purpose?"** \u2192 look for the opening definition sentence\n\u2022 **"Which is NOT required?"** \u2192 find the list and identify the missing/excluded item\n\u2022 **"According to the passage"** \u2192 the answer must be explicitly stated, not inferred\n\u2022 **"What does X examine?"** \u2192 find the direct object of the key verb',null,null,null)
