B.Vj=new A.a1("Readback & Clearance Precision","Translation errors in clearance readbacks are a leading cause of runway incursions. Practice precision in both directions without paraphrasing critical values.")
B.VU=new A.a1("Context-Based Language Transfer","Focus on understanding aviation texts in context rather than word-for-word translation. ICAO language is formulaic \u2014 learn the patterns.")
B.Vq=new A.a1("Safety Communication Accuracy","Translating safety instructions accurately ensures passenger compliance. Focus on official ICAO safety terminology rather than free translation.")
